node.text: Preliminary drop test of our Crystal series. Got final prototypes in today and wow, they look so sharp. 9 feet drops no problem.

Gen-3 prototype looking sleek 🔪😍 Much thinner, lighter, less wide, more comfortable sculpting and fully sealed metal buttons will provide top notch dust resistance. The most advanced construction case for the iPhone 13 lineup, guaranteed. We are working day and night to have these ready for launch. Will have multiple colors & Crystal colors to share soon. Flex on track for next month 🚀

node.text: So grateful to be here, our third product launch. The American dream is still alive for the willing but boy is it a difficult road. node.text: Our upcoming Flex Series pushes side-less case design to the limits. Sleeker, now symmetrical, comfort oriented, signature ‘claw’ durability & powerful MagSafe support. We took our time on sculpting for the best possible design flow on Apple’s new square iPhones. Faithful to the OG, Flex series can balance on ALL 4 sides now 😆👌 Even though these are rough CNC prototypes, we’re very happy with the outcome and are confirming final molds & production. We hope to be shipping these beauties by August. Prices to come, will be very reasonable. (Finals will not have these deep mold lines, just wanted to share our progress in prototyping 👌)

node.text:
Gen-2 Rebel Is FINALLY here. Hey, a May launch is better than August for Gen-1 😅 Here’s everything we’ve improved.

1. Our most durable case. Fully enclosed with built in TPE strips & a new inner TPE sheet for maximum shock resistance.
2. Highest quality materials, tight fit with precise port/camera alignment.
3. Easy to swipe from all directions with our unique corner ‘claws’ providing maximum distance between your screen/rear finish & the ground.
4. Designed for maximum holding comfort with shaved sides, rear palm slants & our signature pinky rest👌
5. Very satisfying button clicks.
6. Improved dust barrier vs Gen-1.
7. MagSafe built in with THE strongest MagSafe holding force on the market!
8. New kevlar texture, now slightly raised for added grip.
9. Genuine FLOLAB NanoArmor screen protector included. (The best glass on the market)
10. We promise you will not get the aesthetics, the quality, the durability for this value from any other brand.

As always, wanted to thank everyone for supporting the dream. From designing, prototyping, refining, launching, let alone staying afloat during a pandemic has been beyond rough. As a small team we are incredibly grateful for everyone’s support and promise to only continue improving. Gen-3 is going to be a HUGE step forward for us, stay tuned 😎
